<div class='titlewrapper'>
<h1 class='title'>
The Heretic's Guide to Global Finance: Hacking the Future of Money
</h1>
</div>
<div class='descriptionwrapper'>
<p class='description'><span>Anarchic Adventures in Arts, Activism, Anthropology and Alternative Economics</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div>
